parser

Interface ContextChange

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Alcatel7x50ParserManager

    public interface ContextChange
    Notifier Interface for context/config mode changes. This is used to notify the ParserManager when context changes from one to another for instance, when the router changes from RouterInterface context to the RouterInterface ingress context. Also used to notify when leaving or entering a new context.
